{"type":"text","timestamp":1775843828343,"sessionID":"ses_28776274dffe9brDjC4IOXgXn5","part":{"id":"prt_d788a3e310010dcJZy6CCb6uNN","messageID":"msg_d788a2cee001a7Ke523vHQyutS","sessionID":"ses_28776274dffe9brDjC4IOXgXn5","type":"text","text":"## AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器\n\n### Completed\n\n**Core Processor (`pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_processor.go`):**\n- `SandboxProcessor` struct with dynamic/k8s clients, pod lister, AR/CI listers\n- `GenerateSessionID()` - generates 18-digit random session IDs\n- `BuildSandboxObject()` - builds Sandbox CR from AgentRuntime spec with labels, annotations, container config, lifecycle (8hr shutdown)\n- `BuildCodeInterpreterSandbox()` - builds Sandbox CR from CodeInterpreter spec\n- `BuildSandboxClaimObject()` - builds SandboxClaim CR for warm pool scenarios\n- `CreateSandbox()` - creates sandbox with 2-min timeout, waits for pod running, resolves PodIP, builds entry points, includes rollback on failure\n- `resolvePodIP()` - resolves pod IP via label selector or owner reference\n- `BuildEntryPoints()` - builds access endpoints from pod IP and target ports\n- Helper funcs: `RandString()`, `GetAgentRuntime()`, `GetCodeInterpreter()`\n\n**Handler (`pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox.go`):**\n- `SandboxHandler` with dependency injection\n- `HandleAgentRuntimeCreate()` - validates request, fetches AgentRuntime, generates session, builds/creates sandbox, returns session info\n- `HandleCodeInterpreterCreate()` - same flow for CodeInterpreter\n\n**Types (`pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types.go`):**\n- `CreateSandboxRequest` with validation (kind: AgentRuntime|CodeInterpreter, name, namespace required)\n- `CreateSandboxResponse` with sessionId, sandboxId, sandboxName, entryPoints\n- `SandboxInfo` - full sandbox metadata\n- `TargetPort` / `SandboxEntryPoint` - endpoint configuration\n\n**Routes (`pkg/workloadmanager/routes.go`):**\n- POST `/v1/agent-runtime` - AgentRuntime sandbox creation\n- POST `/v1/code-interpreter` - CodeInterpreter sandbox creation\n\n**Tests (`pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_processor_test.go`):**\n- Unit tests for RandString, validation, GetAgentRuntime, GetCodeInterpreter, BuildSandboxObject, BuildCodeInterpreterSandbox, BuildEntryPoints, resolvePodIP\n\n### Deferred\n\n- Warm pool implementation (SandboxClaim flow marked but not fully integrated)\n- Sandbox lifecycle management (deletion, scaling policies)\n- Configurable timeout/resource limits\n- Advanced scheduling policies","time":{"start":1775843828341,"end":1775843828341}}}
